Package mklab.JGNN.data

Class IdConverter

java.lang.Object
mklab.JGNN.data.IdConverter
public class IdConverter extends Object
Converts back-and-forth between objects and unique ids and automates one-hot encoding.
Author:
Emmanouil Krasanakis
